# granny-ro-js — local env config
#
# Default `npm test` (the 80 bake-free unit tests) needs NONE of these.
# Copy this file to `.env` and fill in `RO_FOLDER` ONLY if you want to
# run the full 21-fixture live-oracle path :
#
#   npm run setup:oracle    # clone Rasetsuu/blendergranny (one-shot)
#   npm run bake            # extract .gr2 fixtures from data.grf + Wine shim
#   npm run test:live       # JS vs Python vs RAD-DLL parity (629 tests)
#
# See CONTRIBUTING.md for the full setup walkthrough.

# REQUIRED for bake / test:live. Host path to your iRO ver12 client.
# Must contain `data.grf` AND `granny2.dll`. Read-only — the script
# never writes to this folder.
RO_FOLDER=/path/to/your/iRO_client

# OPTIONAL — override the command run by `docker compose run test`.
# Leave commented for the default (npm test, 80 bake-free tests).
# Uncomment for the full live-oracle path :
# TEST_COMMAND=npm run setup:oracle && npm run bake && npm run test:live

# OPTIONAL — checkout location for the Rasetsuu/blendergranny Python
# clean-room oracle. Defaults to ~/.cache/granny-ro-js/blendergranny
# on native runs. Inside Docker, the image bakes it at /blendergranny
# and overrides this via Dockerfile ENV.
# BLENDERGRANNY_PATH=~/.cache/granny-ro-js/blendergranny

# OPTIONAL — override the wine binary used to launch the Win32 shim.
# Defaults to auto-detect :
#   - Linux       : `wine` on PATH (`sudo apt install wine`)
#   - macOS       : probes /Applications/Wine[ Staging].app/Contents/Resources/wine/bin/wine
#                   then /opt/homebrew/bin/wine, /usr/local/bin/wine, PATH
#   - Windows     : N/A — shim runs as native Win32 PE, no wine prefix
# Set explicitly only if your install isn't in the auto-detect list :
# WINE_BIN=/Applications/Wine Staging.app/Contents/Resources/wine/bin/wine

# OPTIONAL — override the path to granny2.dll. Defaults to
# ${RO_FOLDER}/granny2.dll. Set only if the DLL lives outside RO_FOLDER.
# GRANNY2_DLL=/path/to/granny2.dll

# OPTIONAL — override the prebuilt Win32 shim path. Defaults to
# shim/prebuilt/gr2_igc_export.exe (committed). The Dockerfile sets this
# to /shim/gr2_igc_export.exe when running the heavyweight image.
# GR2_IGC_EXPORT_EXE=/path/to/gr2_igc_export.exe
